    "Id": 4,
    "Content": "\n## Changelog\n\nPlease see [CHANGELOG](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/MusahMusah/laravel-multipayment-gateways/main/CHANGELOG.md) for more information on what has changed recently.\n\n## Contributing\n\nPlease see [CONTRIBUTING](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/MusahMusah/laravel-multipayment-gateways/main/CONTRIBUTING.md) for details.\n\n## Security Vulnerabilities\n\nPlease review [our security policy](../../security/policy) on how to report security vulnerabilities.\n\n## Credits\n\n- [MusahMusah](https://github.com/MusahMusah)\n- [Cybernerdie](https://github.com/cybernerdie)\n- [All Contributors](../../contributors)\n\n## License\n\nThe MIT License (MIT). Please see [License File](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/MusahMusah/laravel-multipayment-gateways/main/LICENSE.md) for more information.\n",
    "ContentSha": "ChDL9l48fzq/oIwGT3QQZ5GdHKh7YcedvgBq9fi3iTA=",
    "SectionType": "",
    "StartLine": 0,
    "EndLine": 0,
    "Translation": "\n## 變更日誌\n\n請參閱 [CHANGELOG](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/MusahMusah/laravel-multipayment-gateways/main/CHANGELOG.md) 以獲取近期變更的詳細資訊。\n\n## 貢獻指南\n\n請參閱 [CONTRIBUTING](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/MusahMusah/laravel-multipayment-gateways/main/CONTRIBUTING.md) 以了解詳細說明。\n\n## 安全性漏洞\n\n請參閱 [我們的安全政策](../../security/policy) 了解如何回報安全性漏洞。\n\n## 版權聲明\n\n- [MusahMusah](https://github.com/MusahMusah)\n- [Cybernerdie](https://github.com/cybernerdie)\n- [所有貢獻者](../../contributors)\n\n## 授權條款\n\nMIT 授權條款 (MIT)。請參閱 [授權檔案](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/MusahMusah/laravel-multipayment-gateways/main/LICENSE.md) 以獲取更多資訊。\n",
